"    see \"Bethanechol: Patient drug information\"",
"   </a>",
"   and",
"   <a class=\"drug drug_pediatric\" href=\"UTD.htm?15/58/16291?source=see_link\">",
"    see \"Bethanechol: Pediatric drug information\"",
"   </a>",
"   )",
"   <br/>",
"   For abbreviations and symbols that may be used in Lexicomp (",
